        "## function to plot loss and accuracy\n",

        "def plot_history(history):\n",

        "  plt.legend(['train','test'],loc='upper right')\n",

      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "## learning rate schedule callbacks\n",
        "def simple_decay(epoch,lr):\n",
        "\n",
        "  if epoch<30:\n",
        "    lrate=lr\n",
        "  elif epoch<60:\n",
        "      lrate=0.0005\n",
        "  else:\n",
        "        lrate=0.0001\n",
        "  return lrate"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "sv_Ae2PIgJEA"
      },
      "execution_count": 38,
      "outputs": []
    },

      "source": [
